  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter, national, retrospective chart-review study that will be based on the
      collection of data from electronical or paper-based medical records with available data on
      female patients diagnosed with metastatic brest cancer . The main purpose of this study is to
      provide accurate, evidence based description on the incidence of progression of metastatic
      breast cancer and its clinical management.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Epidemiology and Therapeutic Management of Metastatic Breast Cancer in Romania: A
      retrospective cohort study
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
